id,summary,reporter,owner,description,type,status,priority,milestone,component,resolution,keywords,cc,repo,theme
992,Use X-forwarded-for whenever it is available to set remote IP address,rgrp,rgrp,"At the moment we only use X-forwarded to determine remote user address when remote-addr header is 127.0.0.1. However if a site is behind a cache remote_addr will always be the IP of the cache.

We should fix this by using x-forwarded-for header whenever available and only use remote-addr when it is not available.

Cost: 10m",defect,closed,minor,ckan-v1.3,ckan,fixed,bitesize,,,
